2.11	M._P._Pandit	M. P. Pandit	M. P. Pandit was a prolific writer, and secretary of the Sri Aurobindo Ashram and personal secretary to The Mother. He wrote over 100 books and many articles on the yoga of Sri Aurobindo and The Mother, social and political thought, science, philosophy, religion, mysticism and the classical texts and spiritual traditions of India.	
